296
00:26:07,310 --> 00:26:09,110
She’s out with him all day.

297
00:26:10,160 --> 00:26:11,110
They’re both injured

298
00:26:12,160 --> 00:26:13,280
and in No.1 Hospital now.

299
00:26:14,760 --> 00:26:15,470
What?

300
00:26:15,950 --> 00:26:17,560
