310
00:26:44,760 --> 00:26:45,590
Aunt Jiang,

311
00:26:46,000 --> 00:26:46,590
don’t worry.

312
00:26:47,560 --> 00:26:48,560
Junhao will be fine.

313
00:26:49,400 --> 00:26:50,640
How did this happen?

314
00:26:52,160 --> 00:26:52,590
Don’t know.

315
00:26:54,190 --> 00:26:54,920
Doesn’t seem to be an accident.

316
00:26:55,710 --> 00:26:57,070
I’ll get to the bottom of it.

317
00:27:01,880 --> 00:27:02,640
Doctor,

318
00:27:02,680 --> 00:27:03,880
