319
00:27:04,070 --> 00:27:05,400
The surgery succeeded.

320
00:27:05,830 --> 00:27:06,590
The patient is stable.

321
00:27:07,160 --> 00:27:08,040
He’ll be fine after some rest.

322
00:27:09,400 --> 00:27:09,920
However,

323
00:27:10,680 --> 00:27:11,230
his hippocampus

324
00:27:11,590 --> 00:27:13,110
was severely damaged before.

325
00:27:13,800 --> 00:27:15,070
He’s suffering from a memory disorder,

326
00:27:15,710 --> 00:27:17,430
so it takes time for him to recover.

327
00:27:21,040 --> 00:27:21,520
Thanks.

328
00:27:22,110 --> 00:27:23,050
- You’re welcome. - Thank you.

329
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:29,400
Mom.

330
00:27:30,800 --> 00:27:31,430
Thank goodness,

331
00:27:31,950 --> 00:27:33,070
he’s fine.

332
00:27:57,200 --> 00:27:58,210
Chen.

333
00:28:00,070 --> 00:28:00,760
Shengzhe.

334
00:28:02,590 --> 00:28:03,430
You’re awake.

335
00:28:04,520 --> 00:28:05,230
How do you feel?

336
00:28:24,190 --> 00:28:25,400
Junhao.

337
00:28:30,070 --> 00:28:30,880
Junhao.

338
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:37,000
Junhao.

339
00:28:38,470 --> 00:28:39,190
Junhao.

340
00:28:42,590 --> 00:28:43,520
Junhao.

341
00:28:45,920 --> 00:28:46,920
How do you feel?

342
00:28:50,920 --> 00:28:51,640
Mom.

343
00:28:58,350 --> 00:28:59,560
Yes.

344
00:29:00,190 --> 00:29:01,400
It’s me.

345
00:29:01,880 --> 00:29:03,230
I’m your mom.

346
00:29:07,830 --> 00:29:08,830
Ziqian.

347
00:29:12,040 --> 00:29:12,800
Yunyi.

348
00:29:17,800 --> 00:29:18,560
Junhao.

349
00:29:19,830 --> 00:29:21,710
You remember me?

350
00:29:22,470 --> 00:29:24,310
How could I forget about you?

351
00:29:36,310 --> 00:29:37,590
What’s wrong?

352
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:41,830
What happened to me?

353
00:29:44,590 --> 00:29:45,640
You had a car accident

354
00:29:45,640 --> 00:29:47,000
and were taken to the hospital.

355
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:48,920
The doctor said

356
00:29:49,830 --> 00:29:50,830
you’re fine.

357
00:29:51,920 --> 00:29:53,350
Car accident?

358
00:29:57,760 --> 00:29:59,590
Before the engagement banquet,

359
00:30:01,310 --> 00:30:02,880
I went to pick up the ring.

360
00:30:03,590 --> 00:30:06,070
On my way back to the hotel,

361
00:30:06,830 --> 00:30:08,560
I was hit by a car,

362
00:30:11,590 --> 00:30:15,160
and then fell into the sea.

363
00:30:17,920 --> 00:30:20,040
What happened after that?

364
00:30:24,280 --> 00:30:25,950
After that...

365
00:30:34,680 --> 00:30:35,760
I don’t remember.

366
00:30:38,920 --> 00:30:40,190
It doesn’t matter.

367
00:30:40,400 --> 00:30:41,110
It’s OK.

368
00:30:41,680 --> 00:30:42,760
Just take your time.

369
00:30:43,310 --> 00:30:44,160
I’m glad you’re back.

370
00:30:44,760 --> 00:30:45,560
That’s all that matters.

371
00:30:50,880 --> 00:30:51,520
