372
00:30:55,400 --> 00:30:55,710
Chen.

373
00:30:56,640 --> 00:30:57,400
Where’s Tonghao?

374
00:31:00,190 --> 00:31:01,560
You asked about him right after you woke up.

375
00:31:01,830 --> 00:31:03,280
Aren’t you worried about yourself?

376
00:31:07,110 --> 00:31:08,070
Tonghao was hit by a car.

377
00:31:08,350 --> 00:31:09,000
I need to see him.

378
00:31:09,430 --> 00:31:09,800
Hey,

379
00:31:10,070 --> 00:31:11,310
you’re injured, too.

380
00:31:11,400 --> 00:31:12,610
- What are you doing? - Chen!

381
00:31:12,830 --> 00:31:13,760
Where’s Tonghao?

382
00:31:14,000 --> 00:31:14,760
I’m fine.

383
00:31:15,160 --> 00:31:15,520
You...

384
00:31:18,560 --> 00:31:19,800
Let’s go.

385
00:31:22,160 --> 00:31:22,800
Excuse me,

386
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:23,800
nurse.

387
00:31:23,880 --> 00:31:25,160
Which room is Shan Junhao in?

388
00:31:26,560 --> 00:31:28,880
Floor 6, VIP room.

389
00:31:34,580 --> 00:31:35,340
This...

390
00:31:39,920 --> 00:31:40,520
Yunyi.

391
00:31:44,520 --> 00:31:45,270
