392
00:31:47,350 --> 00:31:49,040
I disappeared during our engagement.

393
00:31:50,110 --> 00:31:51,880
You must’ve been under a lot of pressure.

394
00:31:58,520 --> 00:31:59,560
I’m fine, Junhao.

395
00:32:01,760 --> 00:32:03,880
It’s all over.

396
00:32:04,640 --> 00:32:06,430
Now that you’re back,

397
00:32:06,880 --> 00:32:09,560
we can enjoy our future together.

398
00:32:39,950 --> 00:32:42,590
If you get your memories back one day,

399
00:32:43,800 --> 00:32:45,350
maybe you will forget everything here.

400
00:32:45,830 --> 00:32:47,400
Past is passed.

401
00:32:48,280 --> 00:32:50,350
What we need is to command the present

402
00:32:50,950 --> 00:32:52,760
and live a good life today.

403
00:32:55,070 --> 00:32:56,040
Qianyu.

404
00:32:56,710 --> 00:32:58,070
All my memory

405
00:32:58,280 --> 00:32:59,680
is about Guanmei and you.

406
00:33:00,400 --> 00:33:02,160
Even if my memory will recover one day,

407
00:33:02,520 --> 00:33:03,800
I will not leave here,

408
00:33:05,350 --> 00:33:06,710
or leave you.

409
00:33:22,950 --> 00:33:24,160
When true love appears,

410
00:33:24,830 --> 00:33:27,160
