411
00:33:27,760 --> 00:33:28,760
and can never be taken off.

412
00:33:32,880 --> 00:33:34,710
We belong to different worlds.

413
00:33:34,800 --> 00:33:36,040
You should go home.

414
00:33:36,400 --> 00:33:37,310
Your family is waiting for you.

415
00:33:37,590 --> 00:33:38,920
I won’t.

416
00:33:39,190 --> 00:33:40,190
I won’t leave you.

417
00:33:40,280 --> 00:33:41,640
I only want to be with you.

418
00:34:00,040 --> 00:34:02,000
Tonghao,

419
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:04,950
perhaps,

420
00:34:04,950 --> 00:34:06,640
this is our fate.

421
00:34:08,710 --> 00:34:09,430
Tonghao,

422
00:34:11,390 --> 00:34:12,320
I love you.

423
00:34:34,470 --> 00:34:35,360
What’s up?

424
00:34:35,670 --> 00:34:36,280
Mom.

425
00:34:39,710 --> 00:34:41,000
Where’s my dad?

426
00:34:51,430 --> 00:34:52,230
Ziqian.

427
00:34:53,520 --> 00:34:54,040
Where’s he?

428
00:35:01,120 --> 00:35:02,560
While you were away,

429
00:35:04,600 --> 00:35:06,120
many things happened.

430
00:35:07,360 --> 00:35:08,560
Your father...

431
00:35:10,730 --> 00:35:11,560
What happened?

432
00:35:12,800 --> 00:35:13,520
Your father

433
00:35:14,760 --> 00:35:15,630
passed away.

434
00:35:21,520 --> 00:35:22,850
- Junhao! - Junhao!

435
00:35:22,850 --> 00:35:23,610
Junhao!

436
00:35:24,360 --> 00:35:24,950
Junhao!

437
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:25,800
Calm down.

438
00:35:26,230 --> 00:35:27,150
No, he didn’t.

439
00:35:27,960 --> 00:35:28,580
No.

440
00:35:29,110 --> 00:35:29,840
- Junhao! - Dad.

441
00:35:29,870 --> 00:35:30,390
Junhao!

442
00:35:30,910 --> 00:35:31,470
Junhao!

443
00:35:32,230 --> 00:35:32,760
Calm down.

444
00:35:33,630 --> 00:35:34,870
- It’s OK, Junhao! - Junhao!

445
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:37,160
- Calm down! - Don’t be like this, Junhao!

446
00:35:38,120 --> 00:35:38,760
Calm down.

447
00:35:39,710 --> 00:35:41,280
- Dad didn’t die! - Junhao!

448
00:35:42,150 --> 00:35:42,630
Junhao!

449
00:35:49,190 --> 00:35:49,560
Mom.

450
00:35:51,520 --> 00:35:53,840
Junhao’s been sedated.

451
00:35:54,230 --> 00:35:55,320
He’s fine.

452
00:35:55,710 --> 00:35:56,600
Don’t worry.

453
00:36:01,800 --> 00:36:02,390
Mrs. Shan.

454
00:36:02,470 --> 00:36:03,390
Miss Yunyi.

455
00:36:04,120 --> 00:36:05,520
What about these clothes?

456
00:36:07,800 --> 00:36:08,670
Throw them away.

457
00:36:09,910 --> 00:36:11,190
He won’t wear them again.

458
00:36:11,630 --> 00:36:12,040
By the way,

459
00:36:12,470 --> 00:36:13,390
I found this photo

460
00:36:13,710 --> 00:36:15,630
in his pocket.

461
00:36:26,840 --> 00:36:27,800
You may leave.

462
00:36:32,870 --> 00:36:33,390
Get rid of it.

463
00:36:34,280 --> 00:36:36,120
Don’t let Junhao see it again.

464
00:36:41,470 --> 00:36:42,670
I’m fine, Mom.

465
00:36:43,470 --> 00:36:45,120
Junhao is back

466
00:36:45,910 --> 00:36:47,950
and doesn’t remember things happened in Guanmei.

467
00:36:48,630 --> 00:36:51,040
All this is a pure accident.

468
00:36:51,430 --> 00:36:52,870
It won’t affect our relationship.

469
00:36:56,970 --> 00:36:57,760
Darling,

470
00:36:58,760 --> 00:37:00,120
you shouldn’t have suffered this.

471
00:37:01,840 --> 00:37:02,630
Luckily,

472
00:37:03,040 --> 00:37:04,710
Junhao is back safe and sound.

473
00:37:05,520 --> 00:37:06,320
Look,

474
00:37:06,760 --> 00:37:08,080
I’m on your side

475
00:37:08,520 --> 00:37:10,230
and I’ll make you two marry soon

476
00:37:10,710 --> 00:37:12,430
to avoid further trouble.

477
00:37:26,320 --> 00:37:28,000
Here. Have an orange.

478
00:37:32,390 --> 00:37:32,670
Fine.

479
00:37:33,560 --> 00:37:35,280
What about an apple? Eat it.

480
00:37:37,600 --> 00:37:40,120
Heaven played a cruel joke on Ye Qianyu.

481
00:37:45,760 --> 00:37:46,750
Come in.

482
00:37:55,040 --> 00:37:55,910
Director Xu.

483
00:37:58,120 --> 00:37:59,360
Did I interrupt anything?

484
00:38:00,520 --> 00:38:01,360
No.

485
00:38:02,840 --> 00:38:04,430
You...

486
00:38:05,120 --> 00:38:07,430
I’d like to have a word with Ye Qianyu alone.

487
00:38:07,870 --> 00:38:08,470
Is that OK?

488
00:38:13,320 --> 00:38:14,430
Sure. Sure.

489
00:38:23,120 --> 00:38:23,870
Director Xu.

490
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:29,870
Sorry, I wronged you last time.

491
00:38:34,320 --> 00:38:35,800
Junhao is awake.

492
00:38:38,910 --> 00:38:39,630
I know.

493
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:45,230
I have no idea

494
00:38:45,760 --> 00:38:47,600
what happened between you in Guanmei,

495
00:38:49,430 --> 00:38:49,910
but

496
00:38:51,230 --> 00:38:52,710
now that Junhao is back,

497
00:38:55,080 --> 00:38:57,470
your past should be left behind.

498
00:38:59,080 --> 00:38:59,520
I suggest

499
00:39:00,800 --> 00:39:02,320
you don’t see each other again.

500
00:39:04,950 --> 00:39:05,760
Why?

501
00:39:07,190 --> 00:39:09,040
Junhao is the GM of Senwell

502
00:39:10,080 --> 00:39:12,080
and Fan Yunyi’s fiancé.

503
00:39:13,600 --> 00:39:16,120
Who are you to him and why should he

504
00:39:16,470 --> 00:39:17,120
see you?

505
00:39:23,910 --> 00:39:25,000
You fell in love with Tonghao,

506
00:39:26,320 --> 00:39:28,000
not Shan Junhao.

507
00:39:29,470 --> 00:39:31,470
Your encounter is a sheer accident.

508
00:39:32,710 --> 00:39:33,670
In the end, you’ll have to

509
00:39:33,670 --> 00:39:35,600
go back to your own tracks.

510
00:39:38,950 --> 00:39:40,390
I know it sounds harsh,

511
00:39:43,080 --> 00:39:44,230
but you have to face reality.

512
00:39:49,760 --> 00:39:51,560
Did Shan Junhao send you here?

513
00:40:36,800 --> 00:40:38,120
The accident

514
00:40:41,150 --> 00:40:44,040
separated Dad and me forever.

515
00:40:59,760 --> 00:41:00,950
The job was done poorly.

516
00:41:01,120 --> 00:41:02,870
What if others find out?

517
00:41:03,470 --> 00:41:05,910
Who knew they’d be so clumsy?

518
00:41:07,630 --> 00:41:08,800
Did you pay them?

519
00:41:09,320 --> 00:41:10,320
I had to.

520
00:41:10,630 --> 00:41:11,560
If they leaked it out,

521
00:41:12,080 --> 00:41:12,870
it’d be a bigger disaster.

522
00:41:13,440 --> 00:41:15,080
Hey, I have to say,

523
00:41:15,560 --> 00:41:17,520
you should be more discreet.

524
00:41:17,670 --> 00:41:19,760
Our interests are on the line,

525
00:41:19,910 --> 00:41:20,630
understand?

526
00:41:20,670 --> 00:41:21,560
Yes.

527
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:22,840
Mr. Qiu. Mr. Lin.

528
00:41:24,230 --> 00:41:25,190
Why are you acting suspiciously

529
00:41:25,230 --> 00:41:26,430
outside my office?

530
00:41:26,840 --> 00:41:28,800
We’re waiting for you.

531
00:41:39,080 --> 00:41:39,560
Mr. Zhang,

532
00:41:40,280 --> 00:41:41,800
the Shans have announced

533
00:41:42,120 --> 00:41:44,040
that Shan Junhao is back from abroad.

534
00:41:44,120 --> 00:41:45,670
What should we do?

535
00:41:50,400 --> 00:41:51,730
What’s to worry?

536
00:41:52,360 --> 00:41:55,000
Once he’s back to Senwell,

537
00:41:55,560 --> 00:41:56,800
he won’t allow others

538
00:41:56,870 --> 00:41:58,390
to take his position.

539
00:41:59,040 --> 00:41:59,870
Do you have any solution?

540
00:42:01,560 --> 00:42:02,470
Relax.

541
00:42:02,760 --> 00:42:04,390
The board’s got our back.

542
00:42:04,430 --> 00:42:06,040
Shan Junhao can’t change anything.

543
00:42:07,390 --> 00:42:08,840
As long as you two don’t cause me trouble.

544
00:42:10,080 --> 00:42:11,230
How could we?

545
00:42:11,360 --> 00:42:12,280
We’ve been

546
00:42:12,390 --> 00:42:14,230
on your side all along.

547
00:42:23,470 --> 00:42:24,150
Mr. Zhang.

548
00:42:24,870 --> 00:42:26,390
I heard you took advantage of my absence

549
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:28,840
and did tons of dirty deeds.

550
00:42:37,710 --> 00:42:39,000
Mr. Former Manager,

551
00:42:40,040 --> 00:42:41,520
I heard your so-called research overseas

552
00:42:41,670 --> 00:42:42,910
was quite mysterious.

553
00:42:43,280 --> 00:42:44,390
You know Senwell’s stock price

554
00:42:44,470 --> 00:42:45,710
plunged?

555
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:47,120
Without me,

556
00:42:47,190 --> 00:42:48,710
Senwell would’ve been dead by now.

557
00:42:48,970 --> 00:42:51,800
You took advantage of my mother’s softness

558
00:42:52,520 --> 00:42:54,280
and took over the company.

559
00:42:55,040 --> 00:42:56,600
Don’t sugarcoat it.

560
00:42:56,760 --> 00:42:58,800
I did everything for Senwell.

561
00:42:58,910 --> 00:42:59,840
Don’t forget

562
00:43:00,800 --> 00:43:02,870
I’m still the largest shareholder.

563
00:43:03,000 --> 00:43:03,800
Don’t you forget

564
00:43:04,230 --> 00:43:06,420
the board elected me to be the general manager.

565
00:43:06,520 --> 00:43:07,990
Now that I’m back,

566
00:43:09,140 --> 00:43:10,840
everything will return to normal.

567
00:43:12,120 --> 00:43:12,950
Shan Junhao,

568
00:43:14,000 --> 00:43:15,560
you disappeared all of a sudden

569
00:43:15,600 --> 00:43:16,760
and popped out from nowhere.

570
00:43:18,080 --> 00:43:19,800
This isn’t a peekaboo.

571
00:43:20,040 --> 00:43:21,670
I’ll call for a board meeting

572
00:43:22,600 --> 00:43:24,080
to re-elect the general manager.

573
00:43:24,310 --> 00:43:24,910
Fine.

574
00:43:26,150 --> 00:43:27,470
Bring it on.

575
00:43:49,460 --> 00:43:54,480
♪ Distance between us ♪

576
00:43:57,780 --> 00:44:02,870
♪ Seems short yet long ♪

577
00:44:03,930 --> 00:44:07,910
♪ Heartfelt words are exchanged in diaries ♪

578
00:44:07,930 --> 00:44:11,620
♪ There are no secrets between us ♪

579
00:44:12,170 --> 00:44:19,570
♪ Didn’t get to say I love you so much ♪

580
00:44:20,810 --> 00:44:25,110
♪ You broke into my lonely heart ♪

581
00:44:25,130 --> 00:44:28,890
♪ And lit the fire called love ♪

582
00:44:29,130 --> 00:44:33,370
♪ You drove out all my loneliness ♪

583
00:44:33,390 --> 00:44:36,900
♪ So that I can slowly adjust myself ♪

584
00:44:37,410 --> 00:44:41,570
♪ You painted my life ♪

585
00:44:41,590 --> 00:44:45,170
♪ With flowers ♪

586
00:44:45,190 --> 00:44:49,130
♪ You raised me up ♪

587
00:44:49,150 --> 00:44:52,550
♪ From that moment on ♪

588
00:44:53,080 --> 00:44:55,840
♪ You’ve been singing for me ♪

